      "content": "thanks. but \"rest\" is just temporary. it doesn't solve the actual problem. i look at it like this... if there was a way to just have permanent stillness, wouldn't that be a kind of mercy? like, instead of fighting a losing battle every single day, there's just peace. it honestly feels more like a logical solution than something to be afraid of.",
